features: 【SPACIOUS SPACE FOR YOUR NEEDS】This countertop corner shelf is both practical and beautiful, with a small footprint but large storage space, you can place spices, coffee, snacks, vases, plants, and anything else you need for your life in your kitchen or bathroom. So, what’s your plan ?

【UPGRADED CONSTRUCTION】2 steel legs are added, which is more stable than other single leg shelf. The frame is made of sturdy metal and the brackets are reinforced, this bathroom counter organizer is quite strong in structure and long lasting.

【SPACE SAVING】Kitchen organizers and storage are removable, you have the flexibility to adjust the angle of the shelves to fit your corners or keep them as perfectly horizontal 180° shelves. The multi-angle adjustable design can greatly increase the shelving space for your countertop!!!

【DESIGN HIGHLIGHT】Each of our 3-tier bathroom shelves comes with stainless steel hooks, you can either place your keys, hair bands, jewelry, or small cooking tools such as measuring spoons, peelers, mashed potato scissors, etc. Also equipped with plastic non-slip rubber covers on the bottom of each leg, the 5 plastic non-slip feet also protect the countertop better.

【EASY INSTALLATION】Our package comes with detailed instructions, necessary tools and various accessories required for assembly. The corner shelf you receive has punched metal screw holes, you just need to screw the screws in, you can assemble the kitchen countertop shelf in minutes.

manufacturerProductDescription.media_text: HYNAWIN 3-Tier Kitchen Organizers and Storage with Hooks This countertop organizer for kitchen counter is both practical and beautiful, with a small footprint and large storage space. The countertop corner shelf has been significantly upgraded, our shelves are also very widely used in daily applications, it will become the best organizing assistant in your life, save your storage time and improve your work efficiency！！！

In the living room, you can use this countertop organizer to decorate the living room, stack items, or place keys and other decorations; In the bedroom, this desk shelves can be used as a bookshelf, on which you can place bedtime reading materials and aromatherapy and other sleep-friendly items to improve the quality of sleep and have a good dream; In the office or studio, it can be placed in the pantry to collect coffee beans, cookies and cups as a coffee bar organizer for countertop to recharge your batteries after a hard day's work; In the kitchen, this kitchen counter organizer can be used as a spice rack to organize olive oil bottles, blenders, spice jars, cereals, canned food, salt and pepper grinders, water glasses and other bottles, which can keep your spices on display to save your cooking time; In the bathroom, you can use it as a under sink organizers and storage with which to organize or place towels, cosmetic skin care products and toiletries; On the balcony, it can be used as a plant stand wooden shelf, you can place your favorite small potted plants and flowers to brighten up the balcony.

Industrial Style High-quality vintage wood brings the classic of the old times, and the combination of strong and durable metal can well adapt to a variety of different styles of home decor, brighten up your home! Space Saving Small footprint, large storage space, with reinforced support legs to ensure that the countertop organizer stands firmly and can be angled to fit any space as needed. Easy to assemble In our package, all the accessories and instructions are included, easy to understand, you can easily assemble this countertop organizer in just a few steps.
